<div id="review_1226795924" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1226795924" />
    <a title="Louisa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2618194-louisa"><img alt="Louisa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1302652899p2/2618194.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1226795924?book_show_action=true">Mar 13, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Louisa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Louisa" href="/user/show/2618194-louisa">Louisa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1226795924" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14162737880294308456">Really great book, but I wish I&apos;d known that it was middle grade, because it wasn&apos;t YA. If it&apos;d been Riley&apos;s POV, or just Evangeline&apos;s, instead of Jax&apos;s, then I would have absolutely loved it, but I&apos;m just the reader! </span>
  <span id="freeText14162737880294308456" style="display:none">Really great book, but I wish I'd known that it was middle grade, because it wasn't YA. If it'd been Riley's POV, or just Evangeline's, instead of Jax's, then I would have absolutely loved it, but I'm just the reader! </span>
  <a data-text-id="14162737880294308456" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


